      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIA ZIPPER (3) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Was too tough when scoring last time over 400m at Maitland in a Grade 5 (22.35). Strike rate this distance strong having won six of 11 tries. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Can measure up again. NO SHARES (4) jumped well from the low draw and led all the way to score last start (22.18) at this track in a Grade 5 over 388m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. One of the leading chances again. BLUE CHANELLE (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at The Gardens over 515m behind It's A Tease (30.60) in a Grade 4/5. Deserves plenty of respect. SHREWD ETHICS (8) warrants respect with the drop in distance.",
